name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SmashingDocs - Free Google Docs Templates and Printables

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick access to free templates on SmashingDocs.com.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get instant access to hundreds of professionally designed templates right from your browser with this Chrome extension! There is a template for every need, from business documents like invoices, letterheads, and meeting minutes to educational templates like lesson plans and homeschool schedules.

Need to plan your next big project, organize your home, create a resume or design a certificate for your students? SmashingDocs has it all! The extension makes it incredibly easy to find the right template and get started instantly—just type in what you need or select a category, and you’ll be on your way. Spend less time formatting and more time focusing on what truly matters.

With an intuitive interface and one-click access to 300+ free templates, you can make your documents look professional in no time.
